data.description:
Motivated Seller! Welcome to your dream home in unincorporated St. Charles County, Missouri nestled on a park-like, .61-acre corner lot on a dead-end street. Enjoy highway access while maintaining a serene, rural feel. 

The stunning kitchen boasts a huge center island with seating for 6, newer cabinets and butcher block counters, and gorgeous newer appliances, including a smart refrigerator. 

The expansive 450-square-foot deck provides a perfect place to host summer barbecues, enjoy your morning coffee surrounded by nature, or soak in the peaceful ambiance of your private backyard.

For those who crave additional space, the unfinished walk-up basement with painted ceiling, walls, and floors offers endless possibilities.

This home includes a 3-year-old roof, energy-efficient windows, and a 2-car garage with epoxy flooring.

Don't miss your chance to own this exquisite property in a desirable location. Schedule your showing today and make this house your new home sweet home!
